<HEADLINE> Strong Earthquake Hits Columbia </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SANTA FE DE BOGOTA, April 14 (Xinhua) -- An earthquake of 6.1
grade on the richter scale was registered early Wednesday morning
in the north of Columbia, said National Radio.
</P>
<P>
The epicenter of the telluric movement was in Santos,
Santander. The earthquake was also felt in Bucaramanga, the
capital of the state of Santander. There was no report of material
damage or human injury.
</P>
<P>
There was also a secondary tremor a little after 3:00 a.m.
</P>
