<TEXT>
<P>
Amour has appointed Ali Halil Mirza the Permanent Secretary in
the Ministry of Land, Energy and Environment, and Jafer Ali Juma
Permanent Secretary in the President's Office, the spokesman said
in a statement.
</P>
<P>
The president of Zanzibar, part of the United Republic of
Tanzania, also named Abdi Hanis Abdallah, and Pereira Ali Silima,
as Permanent Secretary in the Ministry of Communications and
Transport, and the Chief Minister's Office, respectively, the
