<TEXT>
<P>
KUWAIT CITY, April 14 (Xinhua) -- The Organization of the Islamic
Conference (OIC) announced Wednesday it has allocated 150,000 U.S.
dollars in relief aid to the Kosovo refugees.
</P>
<P>
