<HEADLINE> HK International Film Festival Closes </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, April 15 (Xinhua) -- The 23rd Hong Kong
International Film Festival which lasted for 16 days was closed
with flying colors Thursday.
</P>
<P>
