The film which won a prize at a film festival in Switzerland in
1998 depicts the complicated feelings and life of a professor
working at an ordinary university in Shanghai, China.
</P>
<P>
A number of well-known directors in the world participated in
the film festival and various kinds of activities such as
exhibitions, symposiums and meetings between directors attracted a
large number of local residents. 
</P>
