up to five years or fined or both.
</P>
<P>
Some 3,000 Anwar supporters demonstrated in several places
Wednesday afternoon and clashed with the police.
</P>
<P>
The demonstrators hurled bricks and Molotov cocktail toward
police personnel, broke several signboards and windscreens of
vehicles and burned garbage cans along the roads.
</P>
<P>
Police fired tear gas and used water canons to disperse the
rioters.
</P>
<P>
The rioting resulted in injuries on several members of the
police and demonstrators.
</P>
<P>
The situation was brought under control completely Wednesday
evening. 
