weeks for its rejection of a peace deal with separatist ethnic
Albanians that would allow NATO troops in Kosovo to enforce the
agreement.
</P>
<P>
Kosovo is a Serbian province in Yugoslavia, and 90 percent of its
population are ethnic Albanians.
</P>
