<HEADLINE> Keegan Confirms Commitment to Fulham </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, April 14 (Xinhua) -- England manager Kevin Keegan has
confirmed that he remains committed to the development of newly
promoted Fulham.
</P>
