<HEADLINE> Dow Reaches New Height But Nasdaq Falls Again </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NEW YORK, April 14 (Xinhua) -- The Dow Jones industrial average
reached its new height Wednesday as investors returned to
manufacturing stocks in belief that the world economy is
recovering.
</P>
<P>
